---
layout: base
pagination:
  data: suburbsList
  size: 1
  alias: suburb
permalink: "suburbs/{{ suburb.slug }}/index.html"
eleventyComputed:
  title: "Mac Repair {{ suburb.name }} | {{ suburb.titleDriver }}"
  description: "Mac repair in {{ suburb.name }}. MacBook and iMac repairs with honest diagnostics and transparent pricing. Battery, screen, data recovery, logic board repair. Workshop based service."
hero: false
---

<h1>Mac Repair in {{ suburb.name }}</h1>

<section class="intro-section">
<p class="intro">If your MacBook or iMac has stopped working properly and you live in {{ suburb.name }}, our independent repair workshop can help. We fix batteries that no longer hold a charge, cracked or flickering screens, keyboards with dead keys, and Macs that won't turn on. Every repair starts with a hands-on diagnostic so you know exactly what's wrong and what it costs before we touch anything.</p>

<p>{{ suburb.introParagraph }}</p>
</section>

<section class="services-section">
<h2>What We Fix</h2>
<ul class="service-list">
{% for item in suburb.whatWeFix %}
  <li><strong>{{ item.name }}</strong> — {{ item.desc }}</li>
{% endfor %}
</ul>
</section>

<section class="common-repairs-section">
<h2>Common Issues We See</h2>
<ul class="repairs-list">
{% for item in suburb.commonIssues %}
  <li>{{ item }}</li>
{% endfor %}
</ul>
</section>

<section class="why-choose-section">
<h2>Why Customers Choose Us</h2>
<ul class="trust-bullets">
{% for item in suburb.whyChoose %}
  <li>{{ item }}</li>
{% endfor %}
</ul>
</section>

<section class="faq-section">
<h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
<div class="faq-list">
{% for faq in suburb.faqs %}
  <div class="faq-item">
    <h3>{{ faq.q }}</h3>
    <p>{{ faq.a }}</p>
  </div>
{% endfor %}
</div>
</section>

<section class="cta-section">
<div class="cta-box">
  <h3>Need Your Mac Repaired?</h3>
  <p>{{ suburb.ctaText }}</p>
  <p class="cta-buttons">
    <a class="btn" href="/pages/booking.html">Book Assessment</a>
    <a class="btn ghost" href="tel:0400454859">Call 0400 454 859</a>
  </p>
</div>
</section>

